Package: rgtm
Type: Package
Title: Manage GTmetrix Tests
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Roman A. Abashin
Maintainer: Roman A. Abashin <roman@romanabashin.com>
Description: This is a library to access the current API of the webspeed test service GTmetrix.com.
    It provides a convenient wrapper to start tests, get reports, and access all kinds of meta data. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/RomanAbashin/rgtm
